gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Kings 133, Pacers 122
gameRecap.excerpt: The Kings defeated the Pacers, 133-122. Domantas Sabonis recorded 26 points (9-14 FG), 11 rebounds and seven assists for the Kings, while De’Aaron Fox added 25 points and six steals in the victory. Bennedict Mathurin notched 31 points, five rebounds and four assists for the Pacers in the losing effort. The Kings improve to 28-19 on the season, while the Pacers fall to 27-23.
